hadiths[73]{hadithnumber,text}:
544,"mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) key sath safar kya, ye log Zohar aur Asr do do rakat padhtey they. na is sey pehley koi namaz padhtey aur na uskey baad . Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : agar main is sey pehley ya uskey baad) sunnat ( namaz padhta to main unhi ( faraaiz ( ko puri padhta . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum usey is tarah Yahya bin saleem hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ye hadees b-tareeq : (عن عبيد الله بن عمر an رجل من آل سراقة an عبد الله بن عمر) bhi marvi hai, 3- aur Atiya Aufi ibne-Umar sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam safar mein namaz sey pehley aur uskey baad nafl padhtey they padhi. , 4- is bab mein umr , Ali , ibne-Abbas , Anas , Imran bin Husain aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 5- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi Sabit hai ke aap aur abu-Bakar o umr (Raziallauh anhum) safar mein qasr kartey they aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi apni khilaafat key shuru mein qasr kartey they, 6- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai, 7- aur Aaisha sey marvi hai ke wo safar mein namaz puri padhti thin padhi. , 8- aur amal usi par hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aur Sahaba kiram sey marvi hai, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai, albatta Shafai kehtey hain ke safar mein qasr karna rukhsat hai, agar koi puri namaz padh ley to jayez hai."
545,"Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey musafir ki namaz key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kya to aap ney do hi rakatein padhein , aur mainey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key sath Haj kya to unhoney bhi do hi rakatein padhin , aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) key sath kya to unhoney bhi do hi rakatein padhin, aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) key sath un ki khilaafat key ibtidaai chhe ya aath salon mein kya to unhoney bhi do hi rakatein padhein . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
546,hamney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Madina mein chaar rakatein padhin padhi. aur zul-Hulefa mein do rakatein padhin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
547,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madina sey Makka key liye nikley , aap ko siwaye Allah rabbul-aalameen key kisi ka khof na tha. ( uskey bawajud (aap ney do hi rakatein padhein padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
548,"Hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Madina sey Makka key liye nikley. aap ney do rakatein padhein, Yahya bin abi Is-haq kehtey hain ke mainey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein kitney din rahey , unhoney kaha das din. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu Anhuma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap apney safar mein Unnis din thehrey aur do rakatein ada kartey rahey. ibne-Abbas kehtey hain, chunanche jab hum Unnis din ya is sey kam thehertey to do rakatein padhtey. aur agar us sey ziyada thehertey to puri padhtey. 4- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney kaha : jo das din thehrey wo puri namaz padhey. 5- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney kaha : jo pandarah din qiyam karey wo puri namaz padhey. aur un sey baara din ka qol bhi marvi (riwayat hua) hai. 6- Saeed bin Musaiyab sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney kaha : jab chaar din qiyam karey to chaar rakat padhey. un sey isey Qatada aur Ata Khurasani ney riwayat kiya hai, aur Dawud bin abi Hind ney un sey iskey khilaf riwayat kiya hai. 7- iskey baad is masle mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-Koofa pandarah din ki tahdeed ki taraf gaey aur in logon ney kaha ke jab wo pandarah din theherney ki niyat kar ley to puri namaz padhey. 8- Auzaai kehtey hain : jab wo baara din theherney ki niyat karey to namaz puri padhey. 9- Malik bin Anas , Shafai , aur Ahmed kehtey hain : jab chaar din theherney ki niyat karey to namaz puri padhey. 10- aur Is-haaq bin Raahviya ki raey hai ke sab sey qawi mazhab ibne-Abbas ki hadees hai, isliye ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, phir ye ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key baad wo is par amal paira (karne wale) rahey jab wo unnis din thehertey to namaz puri padhtey. phir ehle-ilm ka ijmaa' is baat par ho gaya ke musafir jab tak qiyam ki niyat na karey wo qasr karta rahey, agar-che is par kaee saal guzar jaeyn."
549,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney safar kiya, to aap ney unnis din tak do do rakatein padhin, ibne-Abbas kehtey hain : to hum log bhi unnis ya is se kam dino (key safar) mein do-do rakatein padhtey they. aur jab hum is sey ziyada qiyam kartey to chaar rakat padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib Hasan sahih hai."
550,"Main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath atthaara mahiney raha. lekin mainey suraj dhalney key baad Zohar sey pehley ki dono rakatein kabhi bhi aap ko chhodtey nahin dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey iskey barey mein puchha to wo isey sirf Les bin Saad hi ki riwayat sey jaan sakey aur wo Abu Basraa Ghifaari ka naam nahin jaan sakey aur unhoney isey Hasan jana. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam safar mein na namaz sey pehley nafl padhtey they aur na uskey baad. 5- aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhumahi sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain ke aap safar mein nafl padhtey they. 6- phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke baad ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf ho gaya, baaz Sahaba kiram ki raey hui ke aadmi nafl padhey. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain. 7- ehle-ilm key eik giroh ki raey na namaz sey pehley koi nafl padhney ki hai aur na namaz key baad. safar mein jo log nafl nahin padhtey hain unka maqsad rukhsat (chhoot) ko qubul karna hai aur jo nafl padhey to uski badi fazilat hai. yehi aksar ehle-ilm ka qol hai wo safar mein nafl padhney ko pasand kartey hain."
551,Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath safar mein Zohar ki do rakatein padhin aur uskey baad do rakatein. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ibne-Abi Leila ney ye hadees Atiya aur Nafey sey riwayat ki hai aur un dono ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey.
552,"Mainey hazar aur safar dono mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath namaz padhi , mainey aap key sath hazar mein Zohar ki chaar rakatein padhin, aur uskey baad do rakatein , aur safar mein aap key sath Zohar ki do rakatein padhein aur uskey baad do rakatein aur Asr ki do rakatein , aur uskey baad koi chiz nahin padhi. aur maghrib ki safar oaur hazar dono hi mein teen rakatein padhin. na hazar mein koi kami ki na safar mein. ye din ki witr hai aur iskey baad do rakatein padhin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke ibne-Abi Leila ney koi aisi hadees riwayat nahin ki jo merey nazdik is sey ziyada tajjub khez ho, main unki koi riwayat nahin leta."
553,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ghazwae tabuk mein jab suraj dhalney sey pehley kooch kartey to Zohar ko muakhkhar (der) kartey yahan tak ke usey Asr key sath mila detey aur dono ko eik sath padhtey. aur jab suraj dhalney ke baad kooch kartey to Asr ko pehley kar ke Zohar sey mila detey aur Zohar aur Asr ko eik sath padhtey phir rawana hotey. aur jab Maghrib sey pehley kooch farmatey to Maghrib ko muakhkhar (der) kartey yahan tak ke usey Isha key sath mila kar padhtey. aur jab Maghrib ke baad kooch farmatey to Isha ko pehley kar ke Maghrib ke sath mila kar padhtey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- aur sahih ye hai ke Usama sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- isi ke saath ye hadees Ali bin Madeeni ney Ahmed bin Hanbal sey aur Ahmed bin Hanbal ney Quteba sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Umar , Anas , Abdullah bin Amr , Aaisha , ibne-Abbas , Usama bin Zaid aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
554,"Quteba sey ye hadees yani Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Quteba isey riwayat karney mein munfarid (alag) hain hum inkey ilawa kisi ko nahin jantey jisney isey Les sey riwayat kiya ho. 3- Les ki hadees jisey unhoney Yazeed bin abi Habib sey , aur Yazeed ney abu-Tufel sey aur abu-Tufel ney Muaz sey riwayat ki hai gharib hai. 4- ehle-ilm key nazdik Maroof Muaz ki (wo) hadees hai jisey abu Zuber ney abu-Tufel sey aur abu-Tufel ney Muaz sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghazwae tabuk mein Zohar aur Asr ko eik sath aur Maghrib aur Isha ko eik sath jama kiya. 5- isey Qurra bin Khalid, Sufiyan Sory , Malik aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi Abu-Zubair Makki sey riwayat kiya hai. 6- aur isi hadees key mutabiq Shafai ka bhi qol hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke safar mein do namaz ko kisi eik ke waqt mein mila kar eik sath padh leney mein koi harj nahin."
555,"unhen un ki eik biwi padhi. key haalate-Naza (maut ki aakhiri ghadi) mein honey ki khabar di gaee to unhen chalney ki jaldi hui chunanche unhoney maghrib ko muakhkhar kya yahan tak ke shafaq ghaaieb ho gaee , wo sawari sey utar kar maghrib aur Isha dono ko eik sath jama kya, phir logon ko bataya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko jab chalney ki jaldi hoti to aap aisa hi kartey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. Les ki hadees ( raqam 556) jisey unhoney Yazeed bin abi Habib sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih hai."
556,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam barish talab karney key liye logon ko sath ley kar bahar nikley, aap ney unhen do rakat namaz padhaai, jismein aap ney buland aawaz sey qirat ki, apni chadar palti, apney dono haath uthaey aur qibla rukh ho kar barish key liye dua ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas, abu-Huraira, Anas aur abul-Leham (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur usi key Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi qaail hain."
557,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Ehjarizzet  key paas Allah Taala sey barish talab kartey huye dekha۔ aap apni dono hatheliyan uthaey dua farma rahey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Quteba ney is hadees ki sanad mein isi tarah «an abul-Lehm» kaha hai aur hum is hadees key ilawa un ki koi aur hadees nahin jantey jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho 2- Umair, abul-Lehm (Raziallahu anhu) key Mola hain, unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey kaee ahadees riwayat ki hain. aur unhen khud bhi sharfe-sahabiyat hasil hai."
558,"mujhey Waleed bin Aqba ney ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key paas bheja ( Waleed Madiney key ameer they (taake mein un sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key istisqaa key barey mein poochhun , to main unkey paas aaya (aur mainey un sey puchha ( to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam phatey puraney libas mein aajizi kartey huye nikley , yahan tak ke eid gaah aaye , aur aap ney tumharey us khutbey ki tarah khutba nahin diya balke aap barabar dua kerney, gidgidaney aur Allah ki badai bayan karney mein lagey rahey, aur aap ney do rakatein padhin jaisa ke aap eid mein padhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
559,"aagey unhoney isi tarah zikr kya albatta is mein unhoney lafz « منخشعاً » ka izafa kya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur yehi Shafai ka qol hai, wo kehtey hain ke namaz istisqaa eidain ki namaz ki tarah padhi jaeygi . pehli rakat mein saat takbeerein aur dusri mein paanch , aur unhoney ibne-Abbas ki hadees sey istidlaal kya hai, 3- Malik bin Anas sey marvi hai wo kehtey hain ke istisqaa mein eidain ki namaz ki takbeeron ki tarah takbeerein nahin kaheyga , 4- abu-Hanifa Noman kehtey hain ke istisqaa ki koi namaz nahin padhi jaeygi aur na main unhen chadar palatney hi ka hukm deta hun, balke sarey log eik sath dua kerengey aur lot ayengey , 5- unka ye qol sunnat key mukhalif hai."
560,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney suraj girahan ki namaz padhi to aap ney qirat ki, phir rukoo kya, phir qirat ki phir rukoo kya, phir qirat ki phir rukoo kya, teen baar qirat ki aur teen baar rukoo kya, phir do sajdey kiye , aur dusri rakat bhi isi tarah thi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Amr , Noman bin Bashir , Mughira bin Shoba , abu-Masood , abu-Bakra , Samra , abu-Musa Ash-ari , ibne-Masood , Asma bint abi Bakr Siddiq , ibne-Umar , Qabisa Hilali, Jabir bin Abdullah , Abdur-Rehman bin Samra , aur Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey yun bhi riwayat ki hai ke aap ney suraj girahan ki namaz mein chaar sajdon mein chaar rukoo kiye, Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya isi key qaail hain, 4- suraj girahan ki namaz mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai : baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke din mein qirat sirri (khamosh) kerega. baaz ki raey hai ke eidain aur Juma ki tarah is mein bhi jehri (awaz ke sath) qirat kerega. yehi Malik , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke is mein jehri qirat kerey. aur Shafai kehtey hain ke aawaz nahin kerega. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey dono hi qism ki ahadees aai Sabit hain. aap sey ye bhi Sabit hai ke aap ney chaar sajdon mein chaar rukoo kiye. aur ye bhi Sabit hai ke aap ney chaar sajdon mein chhe rukoo kiye, aur ye ehle-ilm key nazdik girahan ki miqdaar key mutabiq hai agar girahan lamba ho jaey to chaar sajdon mein chhe rukoo kerey. ye bhi jayez hai, aur agar chaar sajdon mein chaar hi rukoo karey aur qirat lambi kar dey to bhi jayez hai, hamarey as-haabul-hadees ka khayal hai ke girahan ki namaz jamaat key sath padhey chahey girahan suraj ka ho ya chaand ka."
561,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key zamaney mein suraj girahan laga to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney logon ko namaz padhaai, aur lambi qirat farmaai, phir aap ney rukoo kya to rukoo bhi lamba kya, phir apna sar uthaya aur lambi qirat farmaai, ye pehli qirat sey kam thi, phir rukoo kya aur lamba rukoo kya aur ye pehley rukoo sey halka tha, phir apna sar uthaya aur sajda kya phir isi tarah dusri rakat mein kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi usi hadees ki binaa par kehtey hain ke girahan ki namaz mein chaar sajdon mein chaar rukoo hai. Shafai kehtey hain : pehli rakat mein Sura Fatiha padhey aur Sura Baqra key jitni, agar din ho to sarii qirat karey , phir qirat key barabar lamba rukoo kerey. phir Allahu-akbar keh kar sar uthaey. aur khada rahey jaisey pehley khada tha aur Sura Fatiha padhey aur Aale-Imran key b-qadr qirat karey phir apni qirat key barabar lamba rukoo karey , phir sar uthaey, phir « samiallahu-liman hamida» kahey, phir achi tarah do sajdey kerey. aur har sajdey mein usi qadr thehrey jitna rukoo mein thehra tha, phir khada ho aur Sura Fatiha padhey aur Sura Nisa key jitni qirat karey phir apni qirat key barabar lamba rukoo karey phir Allahu-akbar keh kar apna sar uthaey aur sidha khada ho, phir Sura al-Maeyda key barabar qirat kerey. phir apni qirat key barabar lamba rukoo kerey. phir sar uthaey aur « samiallahu-liman hamida» kahey , phir do sajdey karey phir tashahud padhey aur salam pher dey ."
562,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen girahan ki namaz padhaai to hum aap ki aawaz nahin sun paa rahey they padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Samra ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain. aur yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
563,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney girahan ki namaz padhi aur is mein aap ney buland aawaz sey qirat ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Is-haq Fazari ney bhi usey Sufiyan bin Husen sey isi tarah riwayat kya hai, 3- aur isi hadees key mutabiq Malik bin Anas, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
564,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do girohon mein sey eik giroh ko salaatul-khof eik rakat padhaai aur doosra giroh dushman key samney khada raha , phir ye log paltey, aur un logon ki jagah par jo dushman key muqabil mein they ja kar khadey ho gaey aur jo log dushman key muqabil mein they wo aaye to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen dusri rakat padhaai phir aap ney salam pher diya, phir ye log khadey huye aur unhoney apni eik rakat puri ki. aur) jo eik rakat padh kar dushman key samney chaley gaey they ( wo khadey huye aur unhoney bhi apni eik rakat puri ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih hai, 2- aur Musa bin Aqba ney Nafey sey aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, 3- is bab mein Jabir , Huzefa , Zaid bin Sabit , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Masood , Sehal bin abi Hasma , abu-Ayash Zarqi (unka naam Zaid bin Samit hai) aur abu-Bakra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- Malik bin Anas Salate-khof key barey mein Sehal bin abi Hasma ki hadees ki taraf gaey hain padhi. aur yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai, 5- Ahmed kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey salaate-khof kaee tariqon sey marvi hai, aur main is baab mein sirf eik hi sahih hadees janta hun, mujhey Sehal bin abi Hasma ki hadees pasand hai, 6- isi tarah Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ney bhi kaha hai. wo kehtey hain ke salaate-khof key barey mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayaat Sabit hain, unka khayal hai ke salaate-khof key barey mein jo kuch bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hai, wo sab jayez hai, aur ye sari soorten khof ki miqdaar par mabni hain. Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke hum Sehal bin abi Hasma ki hadees ko dusri hadeeson par foqiyat nahin detey ."
565,"unhoney salaate-khof key barey mein kaha ke Imam qibla rukh khada hoga, aur logon ki eik jamaat uskey sath khadi hogi aur eik jamaat dushman key samney rahegi aur uska rukh dushman ki taraf hoga, Imam unhen eik rakat padhaaeyga, aur dusri eik rakat wo khud apni jagah par padhengey aur khud hi sajdey kerengey, phir ye un logon ki jagah par chaley jaeyngey aur wo un ki jagah aa jaeyngey, ab Imam eik rakat unhen padhaaeyga aur unkey sath do sajdey kerega, is tarah Imam ki do rakatein ho jaeyngi aur un ki eik hi rakat hogi, phir ye eik rakat aur padheingey aur do sajdey kerengey."
566,"aur mujh sey Yahya (al-Qatan) ney kaha : is hadees ko uskey bazu mein likh do mujhey ye hadees yad nahin, lekin ye Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ki hadees ki tarah thi . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey Yahya bin Saeed Ansari ney Qasim bin Muhammad key wastey sey marfoo nahin kya hai, Qasim bin Muhammad key wastey sey Yahya bin Saeed Ansari key talaamiza ney isey isi tarah moqufan riwayat kya hai, albatta Shoba ney isey Abdur-Rehman bin Qasim bin Muhammad key wastey sey marfoo kya hai."
567,"jisney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Salate-khof ada ki, phir unhoney isi tarah zikr kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Malik, Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. 3- neez kaee logon sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney dono jamaaton ko eik eik rakat padhaai, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki do rakatein huin aur logon ki) Imam key sath (eik eik rakat."
568,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath giyara sajdey kiye. un mein sey eik wo tha jo Sura najam mein hai.
569,"Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah inhin alfaz key sath riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye Sufiyan bin Wakee ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai jisey unhoney Abdullah bin Wahab sey riwayat ki hai padhi. , padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Abbas, Abu-Hurera , ibne-Masood , Zaid bin Sabit aur Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- Abu-Darda ki hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Saeed bin abi Hilal ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Saeed ney umr dimashqii sey riwayat ki hai."
570,"hum log ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key paas they unhoney kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : '' aurton ko raat mein masjid janey ki ijazat do '', unkey betey Bilal ney kaha : Allah ki qasam! hum unhen ijazat nahin dengey. wo usey fasad ka zaria bana lengi, to ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : Allah tujhey aisa aisa karey , main kehta hun ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya , aur to kehta hai ke hum unhen ijazat nahin dengey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Masood ki biwi Zenab aur Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
571,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum namaz mein ho to apney daain taraf na thooko, apney peechey ya apney baain taraf ya phir baain paaon key nichey (thooko) ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Tariq (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu-Saeed , ibne-Umar , Anas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka amal usi par hai."
572,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' masjid mein thooknaa gunah hai. aur uska kaffara usey dafn kar dena ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
573,hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath «Sura Iqra» aur «Sura Inshiqaq» mein sajda kya.
574,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey usi key misl marvi hai ke unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. is hadees ki sanad mein chaar Tabe-een padhi. hain, jo eik doosrey sey riwayat kar rahey hain, 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log «Inshiqaq» aur «Sura Iqra» mein sajda karney key qaail hain."
575,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is mein yani Sura Najm mein sajda kya aur musalmanon, mushrikon, jinon aur insanon ney bhi sajda kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, un ki raey mein Sura Najm mein sajda hai, 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke mufassal ki Suraton mein sajda nahin hai. aur yehi Malik bin Anas ka bhi qol hai, lekin pehla qol ziyada sahih hai, Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya usi key qaail hain."
576,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney Sura Najm padhi magar aap ney sajda nahin kya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney is hadees ki taaweel ki hai, unhoney kaha hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sajda isliye nahin kya ke Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ney jis waqt ye Sura padhi to khud unhoney bhi sajda nahin kya, isliye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bhi sajda nahin kya. wo kehtey hain : ye sajda har us shakhs par wajib hai jo usey suney , un logon ney isey chhodney ki ijazat nahin di hai, wo kehtey hain ke aadmi agar usey suney aur wo bila wuzu ho to jab wuzu kar ley to sajda kerey. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain. aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : ye sajda sirf is par hai jo sajda karney ka irada kerey. aur uski khair o barkat ka talabgaar ho, unhoney usey tarak karney ki ijazat di hai, agar wo tarak karna chahey, 3- aur unhoney hadees marfoo yani Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sey jis mein hai mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney Sura Najm padhi , lekin aap ney is mein sajda nahin kya. istidlaal kya hai wo kehtey hain ke agar ye sajda wajib hota to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Zaid ko sajda kiraaey baghair na chhodtey aur khud Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi sajda kartey. aur un logon ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sey bhi istidlaal hai ke unhoney member par sajda ki aayat padhi aur phir utar kar sajda kya, usey doosrey Juma mein phir padha , log sajdey key liye tayyar huye to unhoney kaha : ye hum par farz nahin hai siwaye uskey ke hum chahen to chunanche na to unhoney sajda kya aur na logon ney kya, baaz ehle-ilm usi taraf gaey hain aur yehi Shafai aur Ahmed ka bhi qol hai."
577,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko Sura Suad mein sajda kartey dekha. ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : ye wajib sajdon mein sey nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ehle-ilm ka is mein ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ki raey hai ke is mein sajda karey , Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. aur baaz kehtey hain ke ye eik Nabi ki tauba hai, is mein sajda zaruri nahin."
578,"mainey arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! Sura Haj ko ye sharf bakhsha gaya hai ke is mein do sajdey hain. aap ney farmaya : '' haan , jo ye dono sajdey na karey wo usey na padhey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad koi khas qawi nahin hai, 2- is silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, umr bin Khattab aur ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke Sura Haj ko ye sharf bakhsha gaya hai ke is mein do sajdey hain. ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain, 3- aur baaz ki raey hai ke us main eik sajda hai. ye Sufiyan Sory , Malik aur ehle-koofa ka qol hai."
579,"eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey aaj raat apney ko dekha aur main so raha tha (yani khuwab mein dekha (ke main eik darkht key peechey namaz padh raha hun, mainey sajda kya to merey sajdey key sath us darkht ney bhi sajda kya, phir mainey usey suna , wo keh raha tha :  اللهم اكتب لي بها عندك أجرا وضع عني بها وزرا واجعلها لي عندك ذخرا وتقبلها مني كما تقبلتها من عبدك داود ''aey Allah ! uskey badley to merey liye ajr likh dey , aur uskey badley mera bojh mujh sey hata dey, aur isey merey liye apney paas zakhira bana ley, aur isey mujh sey to isi tarah qubul farma jaisey tu ney apney bandey Dawud sey qubul kya tha ''. Hasan bin Muhammad bin Ubedullah bin abi Yazeed kehtey hain : mujh sey ibne-Jurej ney kaha ke mujh sey tumharey dada ney kaha ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aayate-sajda ki tilawat ki aur sajda kya, ibne-Abbas kehtey hain : to mainey aap ko wesay hi kehtey suna jaisey us shakhs ney us darkht key alfaz bayan kiye they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
580,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam raat key waqt Quran key sajdon kehtey : « سجد وجهي للذي خلقه وشق سمعه وبصره بحوله وقوته» ''merey chehrey ney us zaat ko sajda kya hai jisney usey banaya, aur apni taqat o quwat sey uskey kaan aur uski aankhen phadein''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
581,"Mainey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs apna wazeefa ya iska kuchh hissa padhey baghair so jaey, phir wo usey namaz Fajr sey ley kar Zohar ke darmiyan tak kisi waqt padh ley to ye uskey liye aisey hi likha jaeyga, goya usney isey raat hi mein padha hai.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
582,Muhammad Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya jo shakhs Imam sey pehley apna sar uthata hai is baat sey nahin darta ke Allah uskey sar ko gadhey ka sar bana dey?''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
583,"Muaz bin Jabal Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath maghrib padhtey they, phir apni qom key logon mein lot kar aatey aur un ki imaamat kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hamarey as-haab yani Shafai Ahmed aur Is-haq ka isi par amal hai. ye log kehtey hain ke jab aadmi farz namaz main apni qom ki imaamat karey aur wo is sey pehley ye namaz padh chuka ho to jin logon ney uski iqtida ki hai un ki namaz durust hai. un logon ney Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) key qissey sey jo Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein hai us sey daleel pakdi hai, 3- Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke un sey eik aisey shakhs key barey mein puchha gaya jo masjid mein dakhil huwa aur log namaz Asr mein mashghool they aur wo samajh raha tha ke Zohar hai to usney un ki iqtida (pairvi) kar li, to Abu-Darda ney kaha : uski namaz jayez hai, 4- ehle-koofa ki eik jamaat ka kehna hai ke jab kuch log kisi Imam ki iqtida (pairvi) karen aur wo Asr padh raha ho aur log samajh rahey hon ke wo Zohar padh raha hai aur wo unhen namaz padha dey aur log uski iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padh lein to muqtadi ki namaz faasid hai kyonkey ke Imam ki niyat aur muqtadi ki niyat mukhtalif ho gaee padhi. ."
584,"hum jab dophare mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key peechey namaz padhtey to garmi sey bachney key liye apney kapdon par sajda kartey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir bin Abdullah aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
585,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab Fajr padhtey to apney musalley par bethey rehtey yahan tak ke suraj nikal aata . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
586,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney namaz Fajr jamaat sey padhi phir beth kar Allah ka zikr karta raha yahan tak ke suraj nikal gaya, phir usney do rakatein padhin, to usey eik haj aur eik Umerey ka sawab milega''. wo kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' pura, pura, pura, yani haj o Umerey ka pura sawab''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey (sanad mein mojud Raavi) abu-Zalal key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : wo maqaribul-hadees hain, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke unka naam Hilal hai."
587,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz mein) gardan modey baghair ( tirchhi nazar sey daain aur baeyn dekhtey they aur apni gardan apni peeth key peechey nahin phertey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- Wakee ney apni riwayat mein Fazal bin Musa ki mukhalifat ki hai padhi. ."
588,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz mein tirchhi nazar sey dekhtey they. aagey unhoney isi tarah ki hadees zikr ki . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Anas aur ummul-momenin Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
589,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey merey betey ! namaz mein idhar-udhar ( gardan mod kar) dekhney sey bacho , namaz mein gardan mod kar idhar-udhar dekhna halakat hai, agar dekhna zaruri hi thehrey to nafl namaz mein dekho , na ke farz mein ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
590,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey namaz mein idhar-udhar ( gardan mod kar) dekhney key barey mein puchha to aap ney kaha : '' ye to uchak lena hai, shetan aadmi ki namaz uchak leta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
591,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi namaz padhney aaye aur Imam jis haalat mein ho to wo wohi karey jo Imam kar raha ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum kisi ko nahin jantey jisney usey musnad kya ho siwaye uskey jo us tareeq sey marvi hai, 2- isi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke jab aadmi aaye aur Imam sajdey mein ho to wo bhi sajda karey , lekin jab Imam key sath uska rukoo chhoot gaya ho to uski rakat kafi na hogi. Abdullah bin Mubarak ney bhi isi ko pasand kya hai ke Imam key sath sajda kerey. aur baaz logon sey naqal kya ke shayad wo us sajdey sey apna sar uthata nahin ke bakhsh diya jata hai."
592,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab namaz ki iqaamat keh di jaey to tum us waqt tak na khadey ho jab tak ke mujhey nikal kar aatey na dekh lo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, lekin un ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney logon key khadey ho kar Imam ka intizar karney ko makrooh kaha hai, 4- baaz kehtey hain ke jab Imam masjid mein ho aur namaz khadi kar di jaey to wo log us waqt khadey hun jab muazzan « qad qamatis-salah qad qamatis-salah » kahey , ibne-Mubarak ka yehi qol hai."
593,"main namaz padh raha tha, aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mojud they, abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma ( bhi) aap key sath they, jab main (qaada akhira mein) betha to pehley mainey Allah ki tareef ki phir Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par durood bheja, phir apney liye dua ki, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maango, tumhen diya jaeyga, mang tumhen diya jaeyga''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, 3- ye hadees Ahmed bin Hanbal ney Yahya bin Adam sey mukhtasaran riwayat ki hai."
594,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mohallon mein masjid bananey, unhen saaf rakhney aur khushbu sey basaney ka hukm diya hai."
595,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya, phir aagey isi tarah ki hadees unhoney zikr ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
596,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya, aagey isi tarah ki hadees unhoney zikr ki. Sufiyan kehtey hain : door ya mohallon mein masjiden bananey sey murad qabaayel mein masjiden banana hai."
597,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raat aur din ki namaz do do rakat hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees mein Shoba key talaamiza mein ikhtilaf hai, baaz ney isey marfooan bayan kya hai aur baaz ney moqufan , 2- Abdullah Umri b-tareeq : « Nafey an ibne-Umar an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat ki hai. sahih wohi hai jo ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' raat ki namaz do do rakat hai'' , 3- siqaat ney Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma key wastey sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai, is mein un logon ney din ki namaz ka zikr nahin kya hai padhi. , 4- Ubedullah sey marvi hai, unhoney Nafey sey , aur Nafey ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai ke wo raat ko do do rakat padhtey they aur din ko chaar chaar rakat , 5- us masley mein ehle-ilm mein ikhtilaf hai baaz kehtey hain raat aur din dono ki namaz do do rakat hai, yehi Shafai aur Ahmed ka qol hai, aur baaz kehtey hain : raat ki namaz do do rakat hai, un ki raey mein din ki nafl namaz chaar rakat hai maslan Zohar waghera sey pehley ki chaar nafl rakatein , Sufiyan Sory , ibne-Mubarak , aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
598,"hamney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key din ki namaz key barey mein poochha? to unhoney kaha : tum uski taqat nahin rakhtey, is par hamney kaha : hum mein sey kon iski taqat rakhta hai? to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab suraj us taraf ( yani mashriq ki taraf ( is tarah ho jata jaisey ke Asr key waqt us taraf ( yani maghrib ki taraf ( hota hai to do rakatein padhtey, aur jab suraj us taraf ( mashriq mein) is tarah ho jata jaisey ke us taraf ( maghrib mein) Zohar key waqt hota hai to chaar rakat padhtey , aur chaar rakat Zohar sey pehley padhtey aur do rakat uskey baad aur Asr sey pehley chaar rakat padhney , har do rakat key darmiyan muqarrab farishton aur anbiya o rusul par aur mominon aur musalmanon mein sey jin logon ney un ki perwi ki hai un par salam pher kar fasal kartey."
599,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key din ki nafl namaz key silsiley mein marvi chizon mein sab sey behtar yehi riwayat hai, 3- Abdullah bin Mubarak is hadees ko zaeef qarar detey they. aur hamarey khayal mein unhoney usey sirf isliye zaeef qarar diya hai ke us jaisi hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sirf isi sanad sey. (yani : Aasim bin zamra key wastey sey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey) marvi hai, 4- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : hum Aasim bin zamra ki hadees ko Haris (aa'war) ki hadees sey afzal jantey they."
600,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apni biwiyon ki chaadaron mein namaz nahin padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uski ijazat bhi marvi hai."
601,"main ghar aai , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam namaz padh rahey they aur darwaza band tha, to aap chal kar aaye aur merey liye darwaza khola. phir apni jagah lot gaey, aur unhoney bayan kya ke darwaza qibley ki taraf tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
602,"eik shakhs ney Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey lafz « غَيْرِ آسِنٍ » ya « يَاسِنٍ » key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : kya tum ney uskey ilawa pura Quran padh liya hai? usney kaha : ji haan, unhoney kaha : eik qom usey aisey padhti hai jaisey koi kharab khajoor jhaad raha ho, ye unkey galey sey aagey nahin badhta, main un mutashabeh Suraton ko janta hun jinhen Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mila kar padhtey they. abu-Waeil kehtey hain : hamney Alqama sey poochhney key liye kaha to unhoney ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : unhoney bataya ke ye mufassal ki bees suraten hain padhi. Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam har rakat mein do do suraten mila kar padhtey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : يَاسِنٍ ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
603,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab aadmi wuzu karey aur achi tarah karey , phir namaz key liye nikley, aur usey sirf namaz hi ney nikala , ya kaha uthaya ho, to jo bhi qadam wo chaley ga, Allah uskey badley uska darja badhaeyga, ya uskey badley uska eik gunah kam kerega ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
604,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney bani abdul-Ash'hal ki masjid mein maghrib padhi , kuch log nafl padhney key liye khadey huye, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum log us namaz ko gharon mein padhney ko lazim pakdo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Kaab bin Ajra ki riwayat sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- aur sahih wo hai jo ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam maghrib key baad do rakatin apney ghar mein padhtey they, 3- Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maghrib padhi to aap barabar masjid mein namaz hi padhtey rahey jab tak ke aap ney Isha nahin padh li. is hadees mein is baat ki dalalat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney maghrib key baad do rakat masjid mein padhi hai."
605,"unhoney Islam qubul kya, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen pani aur beri sey ghusl karney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, 2- aur usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke mustahab ye hai ke aadmi jab Islam qubul karey to ghusl karey aur apney kapdey dhoey, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
606,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jinon ki aakhon aur insan ki sharmgahon key darmiyan ka parda ye hai ke jab un mein sey koi pakhana jaey to wo bismillah kahey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. aur iski sanad qawi nahin hai, 2- is silsiley ki bahut si cheezen Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey bhi Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi hain."
607,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qiyamat key din meri ummat ki peshani sajdey sey aur haath paaon wuzu sey chamak rahey hongey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdullah bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat sey ye hadees us tareeq sey Hasan sahih gharib hai.
608,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab wuzu kartey to apni wuzu mein aur jab kanghi kartey to kanghi karney mein aur jab joota pehantey to joota pehnney mein dahiney ( sey shuru karney ( ko pasand farmatey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
609,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' wuzu mein do ratl pani kafi hoga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees un alfaz key sath gharib hai, hum ye hadees sirf shareek hi ki sanad sey jantey hain, 2- Shoba ney Abdullah bin Abdullah bin jabr sey aur unhoney Anas bin Malik sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik makook padhi. sey wuzu , aur paanch makook sey ghusl kartey they 3 - Sufiyan Sory ney basanad « Abdullah bin Esa an Abdullah bin jabr an Anas » riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik mudd 5- sey wuzu aur eik saa 6- sey ghusl kartey they, 7- ye shareek ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
610,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney doodh peetey bachchey key peshab key barey mein farmaya : ''bachey key peshab par chheentey maarey jaeyngey aur bachi ka peshab dhoya jaeyga ''. Qatada kehtey hain : ye us waqt tak hai jab tak dono khana na khaeyn, jab wo khaney lagen to dono ka peshab dhoya jaeyga. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, Hisham Dustwaai ney ye hadees Qatada sey riwayat ki hai aur Saeed bin abi Aruba ney isey Qatada sey moqufan riwayat kya hai, unhoney usey marfoo nahin kya hai."
611,"mainey Jareer bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ko dekha , unhoney wuzu kya aur mozon par masah kya. chunanche mainey un sey us barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha , aap ney wuzu kya aur apney dono mozon par masah kya. mainey un sey puchha : ye Sura al-Maeyda key nuzul sey pehley ki baat hai ya Maeyda key baad ki ? to unhoney kaha : mainey Maeyda key baad hi Islam qubul kya tha."
612,Khalid bin Ziyad sey isi tarah marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai hum usey is tarah muqaatil bin Hayyan ki sanad sey jantey hain unhoney usey shehar bin Hoshab sey riwayat kya hai.
613,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney junbi ko jab wo khana, peena aur sona chahey is baat ki rukhsat di ke wo apni namaz key wuzu ki tarah wuzu kar ley . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
614,"mujh sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aey Kaab bin Ajra ! main tumhen Allah ki panah mein deta hun aisey umra o hukkam sey jo merey baad hongey, jo unkey darwazey par gaya aur unkey jhoot ki tasdeeq ki, aur unkey zulm par unka taawun kya, to wo na mujh sey hai aur na main us sey hon aur na wo hoz par merey paas aayega. aur jo koi unkey darwazey par gaya ya nahin gaya lekin na jhoot mein un ki tasdeeq ki, aur na hi unkey zulm par un ki madad ki, to wo mujh sey hai aur main us sey hun. wo anqarib hoz kausar par merey paas aayega. aey Kaab bin Ajra ! salaat daleel hai, saum mazbut dhaal hai, sadqa gunahon ko bujha deta hai jaisey pani aag ko bujha deta hai, aey Kaab bin Ajra ! jo gosht bhi haram sey parwan chadheyga, aag hi uskey liye ziyada munasib hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees us tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai, hum usey Ubedullah bin Musa hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Ayub bin aaid Taai zaeef gardaney jatey hain aur kaha jata hai ke wo marjiya jaisey khayalat rakhtey they. mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to wo usey sirf Ubedullah bin Musa hi ki sanad sey jantey they aur unhoney usey bahut gharib hadees jana."
615,hum sey usey ibn Numer ney bayan kya unhoney usey Ubedullah bin Musa sey riwayat ki hai aur Ubedullah ney ghalib sey.
616,"mainey abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko hajjatul-wadaa key moqey par khutba detey suna, aap ney farmaya : ''tum apney rab Allah sey daro, paanch waqt ki namaz padho, maah Ramzan key rozey rakho, apney maal ki zakat ada karo, aur ameer ki itaat karo, us sey tum apney rab ki jannat mein dakhil ho jaao gey''. mainey abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap ney kitney baras ki umr mein ye hadees Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suni hai? to unhoney kaha : mainey aap sey ye hadees us waqt suni jab main tees baras ka tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
